      <div resp="part:kuch" type="translation">
        <p n="1"><gap reason="lost"/> by the devotion toward the feet of Śiva <gap reason="lost"/>.</p>
        <p n="3"><gap reason="lost"/> Īśvarāśrama <gap reason="lost"/>.</p>
        <p n="5-6"><gap reason="lost"/> for the maintenance of this <supplied reason="subaudible">
            <foreign>āśrama</foreign>
          </supplied> <gap reason="lost"/> <supplied reason="subaudible">he ?</supplied> gave <gap reason="lost"/> along with elephants, cows and buffaloes <gap reason="lost"/>.</p>
